            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "Thou art about to embrace.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Do not lie—i.e., raise no delusive hopes. (Comp. Isaiah 58:11.) We can imagine the emotion with which this would be said. (Comp. the incredulity of Sarah, Genesis 18:12-13.)",
