      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— She had received this prophet ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "in the name of a prophet, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and now she receives, not a courtier’s reward, in being spoken for to the king, but a prophet’s reward, a signal mercy, given in answer to a prophet’s prayer. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Nay, my lord, do not lie unto thy handmaid — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Do not delude me with vain hopes. She could not believe it for joy. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The woman — bare a son at that season that Elisha had said unto her — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The event, within the time limited, confirmed the truth of the promise. God built up her house in reward of her kindness in building the prophet a chamber.",
        "children": []
