    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "When Elisha conversed with Gehazi still further on the matter, the latter said: \"But she has no son, and her husband is old.\" Elisha then had her called again, and told her when she had entered the door: \"At this time a year hence (חיּה כּעת, lit., at the time when it revives again; see at ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
